#: src/toolbox/tool-dodge-burn.xml:87(keycap)
#: src/toolbox/tool-color-picker.xml:112(term)
#: src/toolbox/tool-brush.xml:181(keycap)
#: src/toolbox/tool-brush.xml:206(keycap)
#: src/toolbox/tool-align.xml:79(keycap)
